metadata.description: When a dream becomes a pixelated reality. When searching for Pokemon in a big city. I tried to create it. Welcome to the world of Pokemon. Pokemon was invented by a Japanese man named Satoshi Tajiri and his friend Ken Sugimori who is an illustrator. In 1982, Satoshi started a magazine called Game Freak with his friends, but after a while he decided to start making his own video games instead of writing about them. The wonderful world of pixel art. Size 4266x4266 pixels.
